General.Name: PNE PCB Bhd
General.Description: PNE PCB Berhad, an investment holding company, manufactures, sells, and trades in printed circuit boards (PCBs) in Brazil, Indonesia, Japan, Vietnam, Malaysia, Singapore, and the People's Republic of China. The company offers single sided, silver through-hole, double-sided non-plated through hole, carbon, and STH and Cupth PCBs, as well as PCB services. It is also involved in property development activities; assembly of the manufactured electronic product; trading of wares and merchandise; and manufacture, sale, and distribution of hand gloves, as well as healthcare supplies. The company supplies its products to customers in various industries, including consumer electronics, information and communications technology, automotive, medical, and manufacturing. PNE PCB Berhad was founded in 1976 and is based in Johor Bahru, Malaysia.
